143
00:07:52,240 --> 00:07:54,080
Then, what about marriage aspiration?

144
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:56,460
Like building a happy family and stuff...

145
00:07:56,460 --> 00:07:59,560
Well, of course I would love to, if possible...

146
00:08:00,760 --> 00:08:02,920
Why are you asking this?

147
00:08:04,560 --> 00:08:07,200
I have a favor to ask you.

148
00:08:07,340 --> 00:08:08,940
It's a proposal.

149
00:08:09,400 --> 00:08:10,580
Well,

150
00:08:10,940 --> 00:08:13,080
