153
00:08:21,460 --> 00:08:25,860
Will you marry me or date me with marriage in mind?

154
00:08:26,400 --> 00:08:27,360
Huh?

155
00:08:28,460 --> 00:08:29,860
Eh?!

156
00:08:31,120 --> 00:08:36,420
I'm actually not interested in marriage, but, my parents keep bugging me so much, it kinda annoys me.

157
00:08:36,520 --> 00:08:39,160
