158
00:08:40,440 --> 00:08:42,520
Ah! You want to have some beer?

159
00:08:43,740 --> 00:08:45,020
Ah, well... eh?

160
00:08:45,220 --> 00:08:47,740
But, why me...?

161
00:08:47,740 --> 00:08:51,180
