168
00:09:08,260 --> 00:09:11,440
Also, your food this morning was really delicious.

169
00:09:13,660 --> 00:09:15,740
Is that all?

170
00:09:16,120 --> 00:09:19,200
Well, including all those, to sum it all up,

171
00:09:19,700 --> 00:09:23,880
