193
00:10:34,960 --> 00:10:36,620
Well, yeah...

194
00:10:36,720 --> 00:10:39,540
Well, if I don't have permission, then I'm just being a pervert.

195
00:10:39,540 --> 00:10:41,900
Eh? I don't mind at all...

196
00:10:42,440 --> 00:10:44,200
I do...

197
00:10:44,200 --> 00:10:45,200
Well...

198
00:10:45,580 --> 00:10:48,360
Hase-san, I'm sorry...

199
00:10:48,520 --> 00:10:55,240
No matter how much your parents are bugging you, I think you shouldn't make important decisions like marriage so lightly.

200
00:10:55,740 --> 00:10:58,660
This was actually my grandpa's house,

201
00:10:58,780 --> 00:11:00,980
but, it belongs to my parents now.

202
00:11:01,820 --> 00:11:03,480
They told me this,

203
00:11:03,740 --> 00:11:07,500
"If you don't get married within one year, get out of here."

204
00:11:07,720 --> 00:11:09,140
Really?

205
00:11:09,140 --> 00:11:11,880
If I get married, they will give me this house,

206
00:11:11,960 --> 00:11:14,260
otherwise, they will sell it.

207
00:11:14,420 --> 00:11:16,720
Then, you should marry Akari instead.

208
00:11:16,820 --> 00:11:20,740
