212
00:11:48,960 --> 00:11:50,560
Hello?

213
00:11:53,000 --> 00:11:54,900
I'm sorry, Terada-san.

214
00:11:55,040 --> 00:11:56,700
You got dragged into my mess.

215
00:11:56,700 --> 00:11:58,700
Ah, that's okay.

216
00:11:58,700 --> 00:12:01,340
But, are you okay with this, Hase-san?

217
00:12:01,580 --> 00:12:02,700
Me?

218
00:12:03,380 --> 00:12:05,900
My feelings don't really matter, that's why I asked you.

219
00:12:05,900 --> 00:12:10,280
Well, I mean, if you meet someone you like in the future,

220
00:12:10,540 --> 00:12:12,680
