244
00:13:44,700 --> 00:13:48,600
To be honest, going out with him was no fun at all.

245
00:13:49,480 --> 00:13:52,060
And the thing I hate the most was...

246
00:13:52,280 --> 00:13:56,040
...the fact that his attitude didn't change at all after dating me.

247
00:13:58,360 --> 00:14:01,640
Somehow, I wanted to crush out his deadpan expression...

248
00:14:02,620 --> 00:14:04,340
Hey, Hongyo...

249
00:14:04,480 --> 00:14:07,480
Have you ever kissed someone before?

250
00:14:08,340 --> 00:14:09,500
