264
00:15:30,300 --> 00:15:34,040
Huh? By the way, Aki, aren't you going out with Hongyo?

265
00:15:34,040 --> 00:15:36,060
Well, he was so boring...

266
00:15:36,520 --> 00:15:38,060
I'd had enough.

267
00:15:39,440 --> 00:15:41,480
I couldn't tell them the truth...

268
00:15:41,640 --> 00:15:43,260
I felt so lame....

269
00:15:43,440 --> 00:15:45,120
I was embarrassed...

270
00:15:49,260 --> 00:15:50,540
It was just...

271
00:15:50,560 --> 00:15:53,400
Hongyo's intense gaze on me was so scary...

272
00:15:54,560 --> 00:15:57,660
So, I kept ignoring him after that...

273
00:15:58,640 --> 00:16:01,240
Then, we graduated just like that...

274
00:16:08,180 --> 00:16:09,800
When I think about it now,

275
00:16:10,320 --> 00:16:13,500
I wonder if that was actually my first setback in life...

276
00:16:14,020 --> 00:16:15,500
I realized...

277
00:16:16,040 --> 00:16:18,380
...that I wasn't that great after all.

278
00:16:27,720 --> 00:16:28,940
Where is Hase?

279
00:16:28,940 --> 00:16:31,480
He went back to the office...

280
00:16:32,420 --> 00:16:33,480
I see.

281
00:16:43,660 --> 00:16:45,480
What happened?

282
00:16:46,540 --> 00:16:51,360
They want me to work on my 4th book as soon as possible,
since the demand is getting higher.

283
00:16:51,540 --> 00:16:57,880
Isn't that good? People are looking forward to your new work.
The 3rd one is also selling really well, right?

284
00:16:58,540 --> 00:17:03,140
That book was just a collection of short stories that I frequently sent to a magazine.

285
00:17:03,560 --> 00:17:08,160
Then, the 2nd one was just spin-off stories that I had compiled before...

286
00:17:08,680 --> 00:17:11,100
It's not like I wrote them from scratch...

287
00:17:11,420 --> 00:17:13,440
Is that so...?

288
00:17:14,520 --> 00:17:19,080
In other words, I haven't been able to wrote a proper story for the last 2 years.

289
00:17:19,440 --> 00:17:20,780
For 2 years?

290
00:17:21,700 --> 00:17:23,080
For 2 years...

291
00:17:24,520 --> 00:17:27,640
I feel like I've heard about this somewhere before...

292
00:17:27,780 --> 00:17:29,060
Yeah...

293
00:17:30,200 --> 00:17:32,260
In other words,

294
00:17:32,260 --> 00:17:36,980
for the last 2 years, I haven't been able to get hard, or write a single novel.

295
00:17:38,500 --> 00:17:40,700
I don't know which one came first,

296
00:17:41,040 --> 00:17:42,960
but they might be related.

297
00:17:45,160 --> 00:17:46,960
I see...

298
00:17:48,240 --> 00:17:49,940
So, Terada-san,

299
00:17:50,240 --> 00:17:52,480
- it's not about sleeping together,
- I'm sorry!

300
00:17:52,900 --> 00:17:55,900
I just remembered I have some works to do!

301
00:17:55,900 --> 00:17:57,380
I'm sorry!

302
00:18:07,800 --> 00:18:09,760
He told me such things...

303
00:18:20,140 --> 00:18:22,480
These are pretty thick...

304
00:18:24,760 --> 00:18:42,040
This is the story of the protagonist "I" and the immortal "She".

305
00:18:48,520 --> 00:18:50,440
I finished them all!

306
00:18:51,000 --> 00:18:52,960
They were so interesting...

307
00:18:53,340 --> 00:18:54,340
Eh?

308
00:18:55,800 --> 00:18:57,640
It's morning already?!

309
00:19:04,160 --> 00:19:07,660
Let's go grab some snacks. Then sleep for a bit.

310
00:19:20,680 --> 00:19:22,140
Hongyo?!

311
00:19:23,680 --> 00:19:26,900
You startled me. What are you doing?

312
00:19:27,500 --> 00:19:29,620
I couldn't sleep...

313
00:19:31,760 --> 00:19:35,520
Now that I have to put a more serious effort into my 4th book...

314
00:19:36,180 --> 00:19:37,860
It's really impossible.

315
00:19:40,860 --> 00:19:44,860
But, I kinda want to read your next book, Hongyo.

316
00:19:46,140 --> 00:19:47,200
Eh?

317
00:19:47,200 --> 00:19:48,480
Did you read them all?

318
00:19:48,480 --> 00:19:55,200
Well, your books are pretty easy to read...

319
00:19:59,760 --> 00:20:01,200
Really?

320
00:20:08,860 --> 00:20:10,120
Hongyo...

321
00:20:11,720 --> 00:20:15,620
If you can't sleep, it will make you feel better when you're lying down...

322
00:20:15,800 --> 00:20:17,620
If you go to your room...

323
00:20:22,940 --> 00:20:24,600
I knew it...

324
00:20:25,680 --> 00:20:27,880
I will only feel calm when I'm with you...

325
00:20:29,880 --> 00:20:31,440
What should I do?

326
00:20:31,880 --> 00:20:33,160
Right now...

327
00:20:33,680 --> 00:20:35,160
I...

328
00:20:35,960 --> 00:20:37,800
..don't hate this.

329
00:20:39,240 --> 00:20:41,200
Hongyo...

330
00:20:41,560 --> 00:20:43,920
...relies on me so much.

331
00:20:45,180 --> 00:20:46,940
Anyway, Hongyo...

332
00:20:49,660 --> 00:20:50,940
Will you be...

333
00:20:51,340 --> 00:20:53,660
...in trouble if you can't write again?

334
00:20:58,660 --> 00:21:00,460
Rather than be in trouble,

335
00:21:03,160 --> 00:21:04,640
I'll be done for.

336
00:21:05,000 --> 00:21:06,640
In many ways...

337
00:21:12,780 --> 00:21:17,620
If you can get that healthy morning back,

338
00:21:20,160 --> 00:21:22,140
will you be able to write again?

339
00:21:24,600 --> 00:21:26,480
I don't know, but,

340
00:21:28,220 --> 00:21:30,740
I think there's still a possibility.

341
00:21:35,180 --> 00:21:36,940
Three more times...

342
00:21:38,540 --> 00:21:39,720
Eh?

343
00:21:42,800 --> 00:21:44,480
I'll help you out,

344
00:21:46,800 --> 00:21:48,440
if it's only three more times...

345
00:21:48,500 --> 00:21:50,020
You mean it?

346
00:21:50,860 --> 00:21:52,620
- Thank you, Terada-san!
- Hey...

347
00:21:52,620 --> 00:21:54,540
Hongyo, let go of me...

348
00:21:59,360 --> 00:22:03,020
Can I move my hand a little bit?

349
00:22:05,720 --> 00:22:07,580
If you don't like it, just tell me.

350
00:22:07,860 --> 00:22:09,580
I will stop right away.

351
00:22:25,580 --> 00:22:27,260
It's amazing.

352
00:22:28,000 --> 00:22:31,300
Your heart is beating so fast.

353
00:22:34,040 --> 00:22:35,680
Well...

354
00:22:37,920 --> 00:22:39,680
You're so soft...

355
00:22:43,680 --> 00:22:45,300
It feels good.

356
00:23:05,980 --> 00:23:07,880
I feel something wet...

357
00:23:08,480 --> 00:23:10,380
...behind my neck.

358
00:23:28,380 --> 00:23:29,660
I'm sorry.

359
00:23:30,180 --> 00:23:33,320
Did it penetrate to your butt?

360
00:23:35,960 --> 00:23:37,320
What do you mean?

361
00:23:39,880 --> 00:23:41,640
I just came.

362
00:23:46,740 --> 00:23:48,880
Eeeehhhhhh~?
